{"tid":1835530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係沒事兒]2020.01.15寄往武漢及鄰近地區的特快專遞服務恢復正常","createTime":"2020-01-23T01:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T03:34:58.000Z","uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"087a7540b157a3d8ac5ce824f77d6b0ae21bef24","tid":1835530,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:27:10.000Z","msg":"寄往武漢及鄰近地區的特快專遞服務恢復正常<br />\n2020.01.15<br />\n香港郵政今日（一月十五日）宣布，寄往武漢及鄰近地區（郵政編碼43XXXX至44XXXX）的特快專遞服務現已恢復正常。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/about_us/whats_new/press_release/index_id_642.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongpost.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout_us%2Fwhats_new%2Fpress_release%2Findex_id_642.html&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzJbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=fa366253\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/about_us/whats_new/press_release/index_id_642.html</a><br />\n<br />\n寄往武漢及鄰近地區的特快專遞服務暫停<br />\n2019.12.24<br />\n因受航空運輸安排影響，寄往武漢及鄰近地區(郵政編碼43XXXX至44XXXX)的特快專遞服務(經濟快遞服務除外)即時暫停，直至另行通告。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/about_us/whats_new/notices/index_id_834.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongpost.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout_us%2Fwhats_new%2Fnotices%2Findex_id_834.html&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzJbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=4dced593\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/about_us/whats_new/notices/index_id_834.html</a><br />\n<br />\n寄往武漢的特快專遞服務暫停<br />\n2019.11.26<br />\n因受航空運輸安排影響，寄往武漢及鄰近地區(郵政編碼43XXXX至44XXXX)的特快專遞服務即時暫停，直至另行通告。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/about_us/whats_new/notices/index_id_812.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongpost.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout_us%2Fwhats_new%2Fnotices%2Findex_id_812.html&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzJbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=0c144607\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/about_us/whats_new/notices/index_id_812.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n寄往武漢的特快專遞服務暫停<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2019.11.15</span><br />\n因受航空運輸安排影響，寄往武漢的特快專遞服務即時暫停，直至另行通告。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/about_us/whats_new/notices/index_id_798.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongpost.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout_us%2Fwhats_new%2Fnotices%2Findex_id_798.html&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzJbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=755d2387\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/about_us/whats_new/notices/index_id_798.html</a>"},{"pid":"e36688136145466499d57707a090f03cf5e256d6","tid":1835530,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:29:29.000Z","msg":"即係已經冇事 大家馬照跑舞照跳"},{"pid":"9afb90fefd74d981fe6d8db2e623b8ea8ebea3a4","tid":1835530,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T03:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}